Table reservations
Bedroom reservations
Gift voucher orders
Mailing Lists | Feedback Forms | Workshop Attendee Forms
As part of the registration process for you to receive newsletters from us, we collect your personal information. We use this information to tell you about the services you have asked us to keep you informed about, to contact you if we need to obtain or provide additional information, to inform you if you have won a prize and to check our records are correct and up-to-date. We will never ever share, sell, lease or trade email lists with other organisations and businesses.
We use a third-party provider,
Airship,
to deliver our marketing newsletters.  We may gather statistics relating to email open-rates and clicks using industry standard technologies to help us monitor and improve our communications, this information however is not personally identifiable. For more information, please see Airship's privacy notice by
clicking here
