Contact us
You may request details of personal information that we hold about you by submitting a Subject Access Request by email to
info@newdawnpubs.co.uk
or in writing to New Dawn Pubs at our registered address, 5 Castle Street, Farnham, Surrey GU9 7HR. All Subject Access Requests will be dealt with as quickly as possible and within one month of receipt.